Class LoadAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.events.LoadAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BrowserListener, LoadListener, java.util.EventListener 

    public abstract class LoadAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements LoadListener
    An abstract adapter class for receiving browser load events.
    用于接收浏览器加载事件的抽象适配器类。
